OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FWords by Lucy L. Middleton
OL,8,FIt's 100 days until the start of the
OL,9,FWorld Cup, where the Iran national
OL,10,Fteam, known by supporters as Team
OL,11,FMelli, is due to play their three
OL,12,Fgroup stage games on US soil.
OL,14,FBut with US-Israeli attacks on Iran
OL,15,Fcontinuing and US Secretary of State
OL,16,FMarco Rubio warning that the "hardest
OL,17,Fhits are yet to come", the nation's
OL,18,Finvolvement in the North American
OL,19,Ftournament this summer has been thrown
OL,20,Finto doubt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
