FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FAt least 787 people have been killed
OL,7,Fin Iran, according to the Iranian Red
OL,8,FCrescent Society, while the US death
OL,9,Ftoll stands at six.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe expanded World Cup - which
OL,17,Ffeatures 16 more teams than the 2022
OL,18,Fcompetition - will kick off across the
OL,19,FUS, Mexico and Canada on June 11, with
OL,20,FIran playing their games in California
OL,21,Fand Seattle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
