OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FITV News takes a look at how the
OL,7,Fconflict could affect Iran's
OL,8,Finvolvement.
OL,10,FWhich countries are competing in the
OL,11,FWorld Cup?
OL,13,FAs of now, 42 teams have qualified for
OL,14,Fthe competition, leaving six places
OL,15,Fstill up for grabs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
