CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FCanada, Mexico and USA automatically
OL,7,Fqualify as hosts of the cup, and they
OL,8,Fwill also be joined by Curacao, Haiti,
OL,9,FPanama, Argentina, Brazil, Colombia,
OL,10,FEcuador, Paraguay and Uruguay from the
OL,11,FAmericas.
OL,13,FIran, Qatar, Saudi Arabia, and Jordan
OL,14,Fhave also secured their places, along
OL,15,Fwith Australia, Japan, South Korea,
OL,16,FUzbekistan, New Zealand from the Asia-
OL,17,FPacific region.
