OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FAfrican teams include Algeria, Cape
OL,7,FVerde, Egypt, Ghana, Cote d'Ivoire,
OL,8,FMorocco, Senegal, South Africa and
OL,9,FTunisia.
OL,11,FEurope has the highest number of
OL,12,Fteams, with England and Scotland
OL,13,Fjoining France, Germany, Austria, the
OL,14,FNetherlands, Belgium, Croatia, Norway,
OL,15,FPortugal, Spain and Switzerland so far.
