OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FFour of the spots left in the
OL,7,Fcompetition will be taken by European
OL,8,Fteams, with Northern Ireland, the
OL,9,FRepublic of Ireland and Wales hoping
OL,10,Fto win a place. Also competing are
OL,11,FTurkey, Romania, Slovakia, Poland,
OL,12,FAlbania, Bosnia and Herzegovina,
OL,13,FDenmark, North Macedonia, Czechia,
OL,14,FSweden and Kosovo.
OL,16,FIraq, the Democratic Republic of the
OL,17,FCongo, Bolivia, Jamaica, New Caledonia
OL,18,Fand Suriname will battle it out for
OL,19,Fthe two remaining places.
OL,21,FWill Iran still play in the tournament?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
