OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FWhile no statement has been made, it
OL,7,Fis thought Iran could boycott the
OL,8,Ftournament for either political or
OL,9,Fsafety reasons.
OL,11,FThe Iran and US teams would come face-
OL,12,Fto-face early in the tournament if
OL,13,Fthey both finish second in their
OL,14,Frespective groups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
