OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FOn Monday, the president of Iran's
OL,7,Ffootball federation, Mehdi Taj, said
OL,8,Fthere "will certainly be a response"
OL,9,Fto the ongoing conflict, but that this
OL,10,Fwould be decided by the nation's top
OL,11,Fsporting officials. He did not say the
OL,12,Fteam would withdraw from playing.
OL,14,F"What is certain is that after this
OL,15,Fattack, we cannot be expected to look
OL,16,Fforward to the World Cup with hope,"
OL,17,FTaj told sports portal Varzesh3.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
