OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FThe killing of Iranian Supreme Leader
OL,7,FAyatollah Ali Khamenei over the
OL,8,Fweekend has left the future of the
OL,9,Fregime uncertain, which also leaves a
OL,10,Fquestion mark over who would sign off
OL,11,Fon any decision about participating.
OL,13,FIran's women's team is currently
OL,14,Fcontinuing to compete in the 2026
OL,15,FWomen's Asian Cup in Australia despite
OL,16,Fthe conflict, and on Monday, social
OL,17,Fmedia videos appeared to show them
OL,18,Fdeclining to sing their national
OL,19,Fanthem ahead of their opening match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FIt is unclear whether the US could or
OL,7,Fwould block Iran from participating in
OL,8,Fthe tournament, and Fifa declined to
OL,9,Fcomment further.
OL,11,FFifa's regulations for the 2026 cup
OL,12,Fsay it is "entitled to issue any
OL,13,Finstructions" made necessary by
OL,14,F"special circumstances that may arise
OL,15,Fin the host countries", but did not
OL,16,Felaborate further.
OL,18,FWhat happens if Iran withdraws?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
