OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FIf Iran does not play in the
OL,7,Ftournament, Fifa could either bring in
OL,8,Fa replacement team or tweak the
OL,9,Fcompetition so that there are only
OL,10,Fthree teams in the nation's group.
OL,12,FWithdrawing from the World Cup
OL,13,Ftypically incurs a fine from Fifa, but
OL,14,Fthe organisation does account for
OL,15,Funforeseen events in its regulations,
OL,16,Falthough it doesn't give examples of
OL,17,Fwhat that includes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
