OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,F"If a Participating Member Association
OL,7,Fwithdraws or a match cannot be played
OL,8,For is abandoned as a result of force
OL,9,Fmajeure, the authorised FIFA
OL,10,Forganising body (including the
OL,11,FTournament Operation Centre) shall
OL,12,Fdecide on the matter at its sole
OL,13,Fdiscretion and take whatever action is
OL,14,Fdeemed necessary," the regulations
OL,15,Fstate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
