OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FTypically teams that leave 30 days
OL,7,Fbefore the first match of the final
OL,8,Fcompetition face a fine of at least
OL,9,F250,000 Swiss francs (around #239,075)
OL,10,Fby the Fifa Disciplinary Committee.
OL,11,FThis amount rises to 500,000 Swiss
OL,12,Ffrancs (about #478,377) for teams that
OL,13,Fdrop out less than 30 days before.
OL,15,FSuch teams would also be required to
OL,16,Freimburse any tournament-related
OL,17,Fpayments they received from Fifa,
OL,18,Fincluding preparation money, and the
OL,19,FFifa Disciplinary Committee can also
OL,20,Fimpose "additional disciplinary
OL,21,Fmeasures" as it sees fit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
