OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FHas the conflict impacted Iran's
OL,7,Fpreparation?
OL,9,FIran's national team frequently train
OL,10,Fat the Iran National Football Camp
OL,11,Fwithin the Azadi Sport Complex, on the
OL,12,Foutskirts of Tehran, less than 20
OL,13,Fkilometres from where Khamenei and
OL,14,Fother senior officials were killed on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
