OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FA 40-day mourning period is currently
OL,7,Fin effect in Iran following Khamenei's
OL,8,Fdeath, and no football matches are
OL,9,Fbeing played. Iran was due to have
OL,10,Ffriendly matches against Nigeria and
OL,11,FCosta Rica in Jordon and Saudi Arabia,
OL,12,Frespectively, this month, and no
OL,13,Fchanges to the games have been
OL,14,Fannounced.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
