OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FMultiple Iranian footballers,
OL,7,Fincluding 2022 World Cup captain
OL,8,FAlireza Jahanbakhsh and current
OL,9,Fcaptain Mehdi Taremi, play for teams
OL,10,Fabroad and, if the situation
OL,11,Fcontinues, could struggle travelling
OL,12,Fback to Iran
OL,14,FIt was announced in February - before
OL,15,Fthe US launched its attack - that the
OL,16,FIranian national team would use
OL,17,FTucson's Kino Sports Complex, in
OL,18,FArizona, as its training base ahead of
OL,19,Fand during the World Cup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
