OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FFacility director Sarah Horvath said
OL,7,Fshe had not heard if the team's plans
OL,8,Fhad changed. "We see sports as a great
OL,9,Funifier," Horvath told US publication
OL,10,FCronkite News.
OL,12,FAt least three footballers were killed
OL,13,Fduring a brutal crackdown that
OL,14,Ffollowed protests against the Iranian
OL,15,Fgovernment in December and January,
OL,16,Fincluding Mojtaba Torshiz, a former
OL,17,Fplayer for Iranian club Tractor
OL,18,FTabriz, who was shot with his wife,
OL,19,FArezou, in northern Iran.
