OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FMasoud Shojaei, former captain of
OL,7,FIran's national team, criticised Fifa
OL,8,Ffollowing news of their deaths,
OL,9,Fwriting on Instagram: "When does FIFA
OL,10,Fplan to react?"
OL,12,FAre there restrictions on Iranians
OL,13,Fentering the US?
OL,15,FNearly all Iranian nationals have been
OL,16,Fbarred from visiting the US since June
OL,17,F2025, under Donald Trump's extended
OL,18,Ftravel ban.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
