OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772625778
OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FThe ban does, however, allow athletes
OL,7,For members of an athletic team,
OL,8,F"including coaches, persons performing
OL,9,Fa necessary support role, and
OL,10,Fimmediate relatives, travelling for
OL,11,Fthe World Cup, Olympics, or other
OL,12,Fmajor sporting event" to enter the
OL,13,Fcountry.
OL,15,FWhat has Fifa said?
OL,17,FFifa directed ITV News to Secretary
OL,18,FGeneral Mattias Grafstrom's comments
OL,19,Fon Saturday that it was "a bit
OL,20,Fpremature" to comment on Iran's World
OL,21,FCup attendance.
