OL,3,CCould war with US and Israel prevent
OL,4,CIran from playing in 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,F"Of course, we will monitor the
OL,7,Fdevelopments around all issues around
OL,8,Fthe world," Grafstrom said following a
OL,9,Fmeeting with the International
OL,10,FFootball Association Board.
OL,12,F"We had the final draw in Washington,
OL,13,Fwhere all teams participated and, of
OL,14,Fcourse, our focus is to have a safe
OL,15,FWorld Cup with everybody
OL,16,Fparticipating."
